elements.name: To validate registration page with different set of invalid credentials

steps.name: Navigate the user to registration page
Pass the first and last name of the user in your name field
Pass the phone number in mobile number field
Pass the password in password field
Click on the verify mobile number button
Navigate the user to login page
Pass the email or phone number in email or mobile number field
Click on continue button
